1. How to write lambda expression
2. 1.8 and upper we can use lambda expression
3. Lambda Expression is an anonymous Function
    -> No name
    -> No Modifier
    -> No Return Type
    ()->{
        System.out.println(); // This is a simple lambda function
    }

   (int a, int b)->{
    return a+b;
   }
4. we can use lambda expression only with functional interfaces



